    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I use 2.7.1 version.\r\n\r\nThis works in your codesandbox, but not in my environment:\r\n\r\n        search.addWidget(\r\n            instantsearch.widgets.hits({\r\n                container: '.hits',\r\n                templates: {\r\n                    empty: 'No results',\r\n                    item: '<strong>Hit {{objectID}}</strong>: {{{_highlightResult.name.value}}}'\r\n                },\r\n                escapeHits: true,\r\n                transformItems: function (items) {\r\n                    return items.map(function (item) {\r\n                        console.log(item);\r\n                        return item;\r\n                    });\r\n                },\r\n            })\r\n        );\r\n\r\nIs it just because of a version difference? Or it have to do with Indexes \"Ranking and Sorting\" configurations?\r\n\r\nEdit: I changed instantsearchjs version in your codesandbox from 2.10.4 to - https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/instantsearch.js@2.7.1/dist/instantsearch.min.js - and now example doesn't work, so looks like it's a version difference. I just wonder now how many things changing from 2.7.1 to 2.10.4 will break for me :D ?\r\n\r\nEdit: I changed version in my code to 2.10.4 and was able to get inside transformItems method.",
